{
  "stem": "23090.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The marktplatz was the center of a city, like if-- how can I say it-- if you live in Shaker, you'd say, everybody has to come to Shaker Square and observe a hanging or a-- some sort of a punishment, because of something that happened, OK?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since the area was comparatively small, it wasn't very far to walk to view, having to go there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you didn't have-- you know when you talk of a ghetto, you talk of maybe the size of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] perhaps not knowing the geographical distances, but I would say it couldn't be bigger-- the whole ghetto couldn't be bigger than half of Solen.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or-- it was that congested and that compact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For people who don't know how big Solen is--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I would say it would be three miles, OK?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it isn't very far to walk three miles, if you're told-- you're made to be-- walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I may be wrong in the, in the numbers, but it always seemed to me that we walked everywhere to, to be-- to be able to, to, to get to the places to-- that we were required and were forced to.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So not specifically knowing distance, and saying that I know-- know that it was just-- This place was a place where everything was, was to be displayed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's that if you committed something against the, the, the rules and the order of, of things, then you were either punished.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or when there were hangings, everyone had to view those hangings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was a participant-- I mean, I was a viewer in, in-- to those hangings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it wasn't something that I was not privy to.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
